{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Night_Away_From_Home",
  "title": "A Night Away From Home",
  "summary": "Restless and a little drunk after stumbling on an old letter, the wandering Corellian Paul Nighman drifts through the Grand Palanhi Hotel and out into Palanhi City, where he trails a striking red-haired woman named Alora to the starport. There he also meets the tearful Major Jessalyn, who is guarding a black YT-1300 freighter, the Black Dragon, and its astromech Artoo. When Paul crudely insults Alora, she reveals herself as a dark Force-user, choking and tormenting him with the Force before knocking him unconscious. Believing Paul subdued, Alora confides in Jessalyn that she is a Jedi made by tragedy -- her two-year-old daughter killed by a Rebel soldier on Corellia -- and that she has come not to harm Luke Skywalker and Leia, but to ask their help, sending word through a courier to arrange a meeting. Jessalyn, masking her own devotion to Luke, agrees to relay the message, and Alora departs. A battered, eavesdropping Paul revives, having overheard everything, and is left nursing his bruised throat and pride as Jessalyn retreats aboard the ship.",
